{
  "doc_id": "FC-LS",
  "source_pdf": "/Users/zwy/毕设/V7/data/raw/FC-LS.pdf",
  "page": 155,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0002",
      "text": " 136",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0003",
      "text": "g) LS_RJT Sequence with OX_ID equal to the OX_ID of the FLOGI.  The D_ID of the LS_RJT",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        57.65,
        540.0,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0004",
      "text": "shall be the N_Port_ID assigned by the Fabric.  If the S_ID in the FLOGI was 000000h, the",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        69.65,
        539.92,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0005",
      "text": "D_ID shall be XXXXXX.  If the S_ID in the FLOGI was 0000h || YY, the D_ID shall be XXXXYY.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        81.65,
        540.03,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0006",
      "text": "If the S_ID in the FLOGI was XXXXXX, the D_ID shall be XXXXXX.  The reason code con-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        93.65,
        540.12,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0007",
      "text": "tained in the Payload determines the Nx_Port’s action.  The Nx_Port may alter the Service Pa-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        105.64,
        540.12,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0008",
      "text": "rameters based on the reason code and originate a new FLOGI.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        117.64,
        405.74,
        128.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0009",
      "text": "h) No Response may indicate a delivery error, e.g., error on the physical transport.  The Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        142.96,
        540.04,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0010",
      "text": "shall perform error recovery per FC-FS-2.  The Nx_Port may originate a new FLOGI after re-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        154.96,
        540.11,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0011",
      "text": "covery.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        166.96,
        154.57,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0012",
      "text": "i)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        190.96,
        111.55,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0013",
      "text": "If the received N_Port_Name is equal to its N_Port_Name, then the Nx_Port is connected to it-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        190.96,
        539.95,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0014",
      "text": "self and this case is outside the scope of this standard.  The FLOGI is discarded.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        202.96,
        479.09,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0015",
      "text": "6.2.2.4  Nx_Port response to FLOGI",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        263.15,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0016",
      "text": "If an Nx_Port receives a FLOGI, the Nx_Port shall respond to the received FLOGI with an LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        540.0,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0017",
      "text": "reply Sequence with the OX_ID equal to the OX_ID of the received FLOGI and the Common Service",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.02,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0018",
      "text": "Parameter Nx_Port/F_Port bit set to zero (i.e., an Nx_Port). This indicates a point-to-point connection",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        539.93,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0019",
      "text": "with another Nx_Port. The D_ID of the LS_ACC shall be the S_ID of the received FLOGI. The Pay-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        540.05,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0020",
      "text": "load shall include the Service Parameters from the received FLOGI with all classes marked invalid,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        539.93,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0021",
      "text": "and the 64-bit N_Port_Name and 64-bit Node_Name of the connected Nx_Port. If the received",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        539.96,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0022",
      "text": "N_Port_Name is less than its N_Port_Name, the Nx_Port proceeds to N_Port Login. If the received",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        539.97,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0023",
      "text": "N_Port_Name is greater than its N_Port_Name, the Nx_Port waits for PLOGI from the attached",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        539.99,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0024",
      "text": "N_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        129.85,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0025",
      "text": "6.2.2.5  Relogin with the Fabric  ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        247.65,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0026",
      "text": "During a Login with the Fabric, if the Nx_Port was previously logged in with the Fabric and the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        539.95,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0027",
      "text": "N_Port_ID,  F_Port_Name, and the Fabric_Name are the same as the previous login, the Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.97,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0028",
      "text": "may continue current communications with other Nx_Ports that it has established logins with; if the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.89,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0029",
      "text": "Nx_Port detects that the N_Port_ID, F_Port_Name, and/or the Fabric_Name has changed since the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        540.03,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0030",
      "text": "last Fabric Login, the Nx_Port shall implicitly logout with all Nx_Ports and wait an R_A_TOV timeout",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        539.99,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0031",
      "text": "period before initiating or accepting communication with other Nx_Ports.  The timeout period shall",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.94,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0032",
      "text": "start when the Nx_Port detects the change.  After waiting the timeout period, new N_Port Logins are",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        539.99,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0033",
      "text": "required before the Nx_Port may communicate with other Nx_Ports. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        398.65,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0034",
      "text": "6.2.3",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        118.22,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0035",
      "text": "SOFs",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        502.96,
        154.28,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0036",
      "text": "Fabric Login shall only be performed in Class 1, 2, or 3. Since the Fabric may not support all three",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        539.96,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0037",
      "text": "classes, the FLOGI Sequence may require retry in a different Class with the appropriate SOF.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        509.77,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0038",
      "text": "Fabric Login is valid for all supported classes as indicated by the validity bits in the FLOGI LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        540.04,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0039",
      "text": "Reply Sequence.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        172.08,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0040",
      "text": "SOF",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        116.55,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0041",
      "text": "c1",
      "bbox": [
        116.52,
        600.76,
        124.98,
        609.66
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0042",
      "text": " may be used to attempt Fabric Login or Fabric Relogin.  SOF",
      "bbox": [
        124.98,
        598.97,
        397.68,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0043",
      "text": "i1",
      "bbox": [
        397.74,
        600.76,
        403.92,
        609.66
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 4
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0044",
      "text": " is not allowed.",
      "bbox": [
        403.98,
        598.97,
        470.0,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 5
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0045",
      "text": "Class 6 shall not be used for Fabric Login since the D_ID field requires an Alias_ID multicast ad-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.97,
        540.13,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0046",
      "text": "dress.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.03,
        123.18,
        646.14
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0047",
      "text": "Selection of the SOF for the FLOGI Sequence is based on the Classes supported by the originating",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        539.92,
        670.14
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0048",
      "text": "Nx_Port.  The FLOGI Sequence is transmitted and the appropriate action is specified in 6.2.2.3.  If an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        540.0,
        682.14
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0049",
      "text": "F_RJT with reason code \"Class of service not supported by entity at FFFFFEh\" is received, another",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        540.09,
        694.14
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p155_s0050",
      "text": "supported SOF shall be attempted until the Login procedure is complete or until all supported SOF",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        695.02,
        539.85,
        706.14
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}